1964;;3 Nuts in Search of a Bolt;;American;;Tommy Noonan;;Mamie Van Doren, Tommy Noonan;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/3_Nuts_in_Search_of_a_Bolt;;An out of work Method actor is hired by a stripper, a male model, and a car salesman to listen to their problems and go see a psychiatrist on their behalf; the three "nuts" lack the funds to see the psychiatrist on their own, hence the request. The actor has to pretend that he alone has all the problems of the three who hired him. The psychiatrist is naturally intrigued and begins secretly recording her sessions with him.